TOO SWEET!!!! If I would ever make this again, I would not use the boxed cake mix. I cut the filling down to 1.5cups of powered sugar, and remained too sweet.

Rating: 3
This was a great do-ahead recipe. I have to admit I was wary when I saw the ingredients included a box of cake mix (I'm not sure that I've ever bought cake mix before!), but the squares were easy to make and a huge hit! I garnished them with a sliced strawberry on each and they looked great.